div.div: If the current user is logged in and this is another user's profile, this button will follow this user, whereas clicking the "Follow" button when not logged in will load the Session Modal Component - this button is replaced with a "Edit Profile" button on the current user's own profile, which loads the Edit Profile Modal Component

div.div: The Photo Grid Component above continues to the end of the page, for as many photos are available (infinite scroll optimizations may be required here - also note that the somewhat redundant "Discover" link above is a prime location to implement the "Map" link bonus-feature that enables location-based photo discovery via the Google Maps API)
